Package: BrownianMotion
Type: Package
Title: Brownian Motion Simulations
Version: 0.3.0
Authors@R: c(person("Louis", "Aslett", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                    email = "louis.aslett@durham.ac.uk"),
             person("Murray", "Pollock", role = "aut",
                    email = "murray.pollock@gmail.com")) 
Description: An implementation of algorithms for simulation of (multivariate)
  Brownian motion trajectories, including simple unconditional simulation,
  Brownian bridges, as well as layered and localised Brownian motion simulators.
